longBusinessSummary: Viscom AG develops, manufactures, and sells automated inspection systems in Europe, the Americas, Asia, and internationally. It offers solder paste, optical, conformal coating, manual X-ray/CT and bond inspection systems, as well as software solutions. The company also provides conversion and modernization, as well as application support, training, and maintenance services. Its inspection solutions are used in various industries, such as automotive electronics, aerospace engineering, industrial and consumer electronics, medical technology, telecommunications, and energy storage. The company was founded in 1984 and is headquartered in Hanover, Germany. Viscom AG is a subsidiary of HPC VermÃ¶gensverwaltung GmbH.
